 # DevSecOps-K8s-Three-Tier-App

🚀 A Secure, Scalable, and Production-Ready Three-Tier Web Application with DevSecOps Practices on Kubernetes

📌 Overview
This project implements a Three-Tier Web Application with DevSecOps best practices, ensuring security, automation, and observability in a Kubernetes environment.

🛠️ Architecture Diagram

                    +--------------------------+
                    |        User Access        |
                    +-----------+--------------+
                                |
                     ┌──────────▼──────────┐
                     │    Load Balancer     │
                     │ (Nginx / Ingress)    │
                     └──────────┬──────────┘
                                |
           ┌───────────────────▼───────────────────┐
           │             Frontend (UI)             │
           │ (React / Angular / Vue)               │
           └───────────────────┬───────────────────┘
                                |
           ┌───────────────────▼───────────────────┐
           │           Backend (API Layer)         │
           │ (Node.js / Flask / Django)            │
           └───────────────────┬───────────────────┘
                                |
           ┌───────────────────▼───────────────────┐
           │           Database Layer              │
           │ (PostgreSQL / MySQL / MongoDB)        │
           └───────────────────────────────────────┘

